parameters:
\F[sirius_angry2]Akane: "The Emperor's New Clothes... it feels a bit off, but
if you're satisfied, then it's fine."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Does this mean... everything will go back to
normal?"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Yeah. We've defeated all the monsters. This lewd
'kingdom' is finished."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[ayaka_susmile]\AA[2]Ayaka: "Welcome back. It seems like it went well."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[ajiri_nasi]\AA[2]Yui: "You don't look like it. A skilled agent who defeated
Poison all by herself."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[ajiri_nasi]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko, lending me the suit... it saved me. I
couldn't have won without it."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "So the incident has been resolved... Anyway... good
work."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "I was worried. I'm glad you're okay... you seem
well..."
\F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "How should I put it... are you okay?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "The feelings you gave me... they formed this
kingdom... I thought you would accept it..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "It's just like you to ruin everything by not being
honest... but still... you needed this 'kingdom'!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Here... I could have confessed! I could have
whispered my love to the person I adore without any shame!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's what you wanted to do... right? I wasn't
wrong..."

???: "Indeed. You are not wrong. The 'kingdom' is
necessary."

\F[sirius_damage]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[2]???: "Gufufu! With a 'kingdom' where one can unleash their
sexual desires, our plans can progress even further! To the
point where we can defeat that detestable woman...!"

\F[ajiri_angry2]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[1]Yui: "Rivildo!? So the rumors about them skulking around the
academy were true..."
\F[sirius_damage]Akane: "Ugh...! It's burning like I've been stabbed...!!"

\F[ayaka_sutrouble]Ayaka: "She's been hit with the Poison Stamp!? Quick... use
Strong Burst to stop it...!!"

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[2]Okashimakuru: "Stop right there! Shiratora Nadeshiko.
Gufufu, such a slut doesn't suit you. You'd be better off as
part of my... Semen Doll Collection."

\F[nako_crytyu]Nadeshiko: "The culprit... he had a large body and was
looming over me... wearing a mask..."

\F[nako_crytyu]Nadeshiko: "Sob... and he said he would make me part of
his... collection..."

\FF[okasi_magu]Okashimakuru: "Between the bitch who's awakened to reverse
roles, and the student council president, you've ruined the
best prospects. You'll take responsibility yourself! I know
what you desire."
\F[sirius_damage]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[1]Akane: "You... guh... what did you do to Nadeshiko!"

\F[sirius_damage]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[2]Okashimakuru: "You want to be... released from your pathetic
self, don't you?"

\F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "(There's no way I can do that... I can't make
Nadeshiko sad...)"

\F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "(Even with me around... in the end, I can't protect
Nadeshiko...)"

\F[beni_troubletyu]Akane: "I don't want this... I don't want to see Nadeshiko
sad because of me..."

\F[beni_troubletyu]Akane: "I, who can't do anything... have no right to be by
her side..."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "My desire to be with her... only ends up hurting
Nadeshiko..."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[okasi_magu]\AA[2]Okashimakuru: "Oh! What a malevolent form!! I can feel an
evil power that swallows everything...!"

\F[ayaka_suangry]Ayaka: "This power... it feels dangerous...! But... I'll
save you! Akane-san!"

Vega: "I never thought I'd have to fight my senior... this
is youth! I'll help you out, big sis!"
